Combine garlic, mayonnaise, lemon zest, lemon juice, and red wine vinegar in a medium bowl. Slowly whisk in the oil until emulsified and season with salt and pepper. Combine the cucumber, tomatoes, onion, feta, romaine and parsley in a bowl. Add some of the dressing and toss to coat, season with salt and pepper. Spread some of the dressing over the entire surface of the bread, top with some of the salad, roll and eat or serve open face on a large plate.